cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and machine translation. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves the use of neural networks for translation. Additionally, it may be relevant to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves the use of neural networks, and cs.CV (Computer Vision) as it involves image captioning, which is a related task to machine translation.
